==English==

===Noun===
'''tenure'''   (plural ''[[tenures]]'')
# the status of [[possessing]] a thing or an office; an [[incumbency]]
# the [[period]] of time during which it is possessed
# the status of having a [[permanent]] post at an [[academic]] [[institution]]
# the [[right]] to hold [[land]] under the [[feudal system]]

